## Safety nets installed

- `PreToolUse` Bash guard (blocks destructive commands) — `.claude/hooks/block-destructive.sh`
- `PreToolUse` Edit/Write guard (blocks secret writes) — `.claude/hooks/protect-secrets.sh`
- Per-subproject `.claude/` overrides take precedence (don't load this CLAUDE.md inside them)
